        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-05-29T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-05-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="601" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d601">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">865.00/5–2946: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Italy</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Key</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-05-29">May 29,
                            1946</date>.<lb/>[Received May 30—5:18 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2690. Most papers carry news that Allies have declared that institutional truce
                    is at an end. Press quotes from following <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> communiqué: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“In conformity to declarations made some weeks ago in London and
                            Washington President of Allied Commission Ellery Stone has in last few
                            days officially confirmed to De Gasperi that Allied Governments in view
                            of imminent elections regard pledge made by various Italian Governments
                            that have been in power since Armistice relative to institutional truce
                            no longer in force.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Sent Dept 2690; repeated Caserta 796; Paris 297.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Key</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
